{"tid":1554264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再放fake news喇 冇咩必要同共產黨玩泥漿摔角","createTime":"2019-09-09T01:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T16:54:06.000Z","uid":254123,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f4db6a39946ac8f2e267d454db968d626763e2","tid":1554264,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"第一 我地行得正企得正，冇咩必要污名化自己。<br />\n<br />\n第二 玩抺黑真係好老土既政治遊戲，你一齊玩只會令自己都跌落泥沼，水洗都唔清。<br />\n<br />\n第三 永遠不要和白痴爭辯。因為他會把你的智商拉到和他同一水平，然後用豐富的經驗打敗你。"},{"pid":"390472948a2feb942e117a47c6999ea4ecdbbd8f","tid":1554264,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df3c7f43291967a3e9bb35a5cf73e72459f367f5","tid":1554264,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c97da03fadc5439d5020c743188adf5c632d350","tid":1554264,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"4693ac6a6e30d19cc8f1f3c2f7dfdf944f686c42","tid":1554264,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"對家就係想我地同佢地argue d無聊野呀 唔好上當"},{"pid":"297082fb987de4817f1ab89d9e99427088cf5364","tid":1554264,"uid":23046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"根本鬥無賴唔會夠佢黎<br />\n佢在明在暗都耍緊無賴<br />\n同埋我地對象又唔係無賴既人<br />\n冇必要呃人，令信我地既人唔企我地呢邊<br />\n唔係民唔民意既問題<br />\n亦唔係咩仲同無賴中共講道德<br />\n唔係要輸得有尊嚴有光環<br />\n而係要令幫我地既人幫得落手<br />\n明唔明"},{"pid":"f0cedb551eba36746525c1eac548d7ce4872c072","tid":1554264,"uid":184801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"Agree<br />\n失信於人就唔會有其他人幫你"},{"pid":"07fd28e41c383038ff318b2ddb97eb1aa12ad745","tid":1554264,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"同意 咬死啲真野 eg 721